    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of medium-sized tree native to the western and southwestern Mediterranean region. It is widely planted for timber in its native area, being one of the most important trees in forestry in France, Spain and Portugal. Also used as an ornamental and for medicine and turpentine.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
